Definition: in an offensive and hateful manner
Example: I don't know anyone who could have behaved so abominably
Synonyms: adj, all, offensive, detestable, repulsively, repulsive, abominably, hateful, abominable, odiously, odious, in, an, and, manner, I, don, t, know, anyone, who, could, have, behaved, so
Category: adv.all
